ent-AU14prodigyclothingequipmentvendor = Prodigy Security Forces apparel vendor
    .desc =
        An automated dispenser rack, hooked up to a small storage of Security Forces apparel from the Prodigy Corporation. Standard issue aboard naval vessels, military outposts, corporate-science installations and civilian colonies across the frontier. Manufactured to outfit personnel rapidly following cryogenic hypersleep or emergency mobilization.
        For full operational readiness, select one item from each section: fatigues with a webbing, footwear, gloves, headgear, armor, backpack, belt and a pouch.
ent-AU14prodigyequipmentvendor = Prodigy Security Forces equipment vendor
    .desc =
        An automated dispenser rack, hooked up to a small storage of Security Forces equipment from the Prodigy Corporation. Stocked with medical supplies and field gear for rapid deployment following cryogenic hypersleep or emergency mobilization. The interface is intentionally simple, even someone with tunnel-vision and frostbite can operate it.
        Rapid-issue protocol: prioritize medical supplies, a ration pack, an e-tool and sandbags.
ent-AU14prodigycorpsmanvendor = Prodigy Security Forces medical vendor
    .desc =
        An automated medical rack, hooked up to a compact stock of Security Forces trauma supplies from the Prodigy Corporation. Standard issue for corpsmen aboard naval vessels, outposts and colonies where casualties arrive faster than reinforcements. Designed for rapid reconstitution of combat medics following cryogenic hypersleep or emergency call-up.
        Corpsman protocol: select the essential equipment set, storage and limited medications.
ent-AU14prodigyaircrewvendor = Prodigy Security Forces aircrew vendor
    .desc =
        An automated dispenser rack, hooked up to a small storage of Security Forces aircrew flight and support gear from the Prodigy Corporation. Engineered to get flight personnel flight-ready in seconds after cryogenic hypersleep or scramble orders.
        Aircrew protocol: select a set of fatigues, the essential medical equipment and storage kit.
ent-AU14prodigycommandequipmentvendor = Prodigy Security Forces command vendor
    .desc = An automated command rack, hooked up to a restricted storage of Security Forces command-leadership equipment from the Prodigy Corporation. Manufactured to equip commanding personnel following cryogenic hypersleep or an emergency directive is issued.
ent-AU14prodigySGequipmentvendor = Prodigy Security Forces smartgunner equipment vendor
    .desc = An automated smartgunner rack, hooked up to a small armory of Security Forces heavy-weapon operator systems from the Prodigy Corporation. Standard issue for designated smart-gun crews on naval vessels and high-threat outposts. Built to bring heavy fire support online rapidly after cryogenic hypersleep or emergency mobilization.
ent-AU14prodigysectionleaderequipmentvendor = Prodigy Security Forces section leader vendor
    .desc = An automated equipment rack, hooked up to a compact storage of Security Forces section-leadership equipment from the Prodigy Corporation. Designed for immediate readiness following cryogenic hypersleep or rapid mobilization orders.
ent-AU14prodigyWeaponsVendor = Prodigy Security Forces weapons rack
    .desc =
        An automated weapons rack, hooked up to a small armory of Security Forces weaponry from the Prodigy Corporation. Standard issue across the frontier where threats can appear without warning. Engineered to arm personnel in seconds following cryogenic hypersleep or emergency mobilization.
        For immediate combat readiness: select a primary weapon kit and a sidearm.
ent-AU14prodigySpecialWeaponsVendor = Prodigy Security Forces special weapons rack
    .desc =
        An automated special weapons rack, hooked up to a restricted armory of Security Forces heavy and breaching ordnance from the Prodigy Corporation. Standard issue only for qualified operators. Engineered to deliver overwhelming firepower the instant cryogenic hypersleep ends or an emergency mobilization is called.
        Special weapons protocol: one weapon system of choice with a full ammunition loadout and explosives.
ent-AU14ProdigyRequisitionVendor = prodigy automated requisitions vendor
    .desc = An automated supply rack hooked up to a big storage of various firearms, ammunitions, explosives, load carrying equipment and other miscellaneous items.
